reviewText: Not bad first time govinda,did some thing new it was scary.

I really enjoyed this movie.  The reference to Sergio Leone was so tongue in cheek.  However, I am a huge Ranveer Singh fan.  I think it is worth watching just for the opening song and dance.  I highly recommend this film.

I love Bollywood and I really liked the film. Govinda has a future as a goonda. He did not get enough dance time however. Ali Zafar was regulated to second place ans he really stole the show in many ways.
This movie probably won't be noted in film history. Or maybe it will. I don't know. I thought it was goofy, campy, and delicious. I have it for dinner every now-and-then.
